# scripts/ — execution entry points
#
# Scripts wire together src/ modules and are run directly (CLI, cron, etc.).
# No business logic here — only orchestration and I/O wiring.
#
# Naming: verb_noun.py  (e.g. run_pipeline.py, export_report.py, fetch_data.py)
# Each script should be runnable standalone: python scripts/run_pipeline.py
